### Get Customer Analytics Overview
# Customer segmentation and behavior insights
# @name customers-overview
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/customers

###

### Get Customer Analytics - RFM Segments
# Customer segmentation using RFM analysis (Recency, Frequency, Monetary)
# @name customers-rfm
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/customers?segment_type=rfm

###

### Get Customer Analytics - Acquisition Channel
# Customer breakdown by acquisition channel
# @name customers-channel
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/customers?segment_type=acquisition_channel

###

### Get Customer Analytics - Top Customers
# Top 20 customers by lifetime value
# @name customers-top
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/analytics/customers?limit=20